      "span_text": "The largest intervention trial in patients who received curative treatment for stage I and II SCCHN accrued at the same time as our trial.  Given the high toxicity rate with the 50 to 100 mg/m 2 body surface area dose, a lower daily dose of isotretinoin (30 mg) or placebo was received for a longer duration (3 years)."
